r a while, but will reset at some point.  Bards and rogues are able to sense and disarm traps, so if you know there's traps about it's always a good idea to have some of them on hand <p><center><IMG SRC=http://namsun.homestead.com/files/eqpics/namsunsig2.jpg><br>
