<br>
The best way to find them (without hurting yourself) is a bard or rogue. The best way to pass them is a rogue (or bard, but I don't remember how effective their disarm traps really is).<br>
<br>
The only time they're seriously dangerous to a monk is when you feign too close to one, and it resets and zaps you out of feign (usually because someone else ran past it). Not a happy thing in DN.<br>
